  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Supports up to four players in online play<br></li><li> Over a dozen controllable characters to choose from<br></li><li> Over a hundred types of items available for players to choose from<br></li><li> Create your own unique build!<br></li><li> Side-scrolling roguelite adventure game</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are more than a dozen controllable characters in the game each with 1 special attack and 4 skills. Each skill can evolve into 3 variants! You can personalize each character until you find the one that suits you best!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Portal Dungeon is a side-scrolling Roguelite game. There are currently eight levels in total, with each level having very different maps, monsters, and bosses. How will you take on these different enemies with their different styles of fighting?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are hundreds of items in the game with no limit to the number of items you can take, so there's no need to worry about carrying to many of any one item. You can equip items as you wish and use them as main items in conjunction with character talents to form your own unique build as you bravely venture forth into the world of Portal Dungeon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Supports single player and up to 4 players connected online. It's more fun to take on the dungeon with friends!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1dad10cf72569020be22224843e3196c.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Supports up to four players in online play<br></li><li> Over a dozen controllable characters to choose from<br></li><li> Over a hundred types of items available for players to choose from<br></li><li> Create your own unique build!<br></li><li> Side-scrolling roguelite adventure game</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/3fcdb1f57e48af8d724b691443ba2733.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are more than a dozen controllable characters in the game each with 1 special attack and 4 skills. Each skill can evolve into 3 variants! You can personalize each character until you find the one that suits you best!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/2604107052d3b88c7c7db017b308e481.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Portal Dungeon is a side-scrolling Roguelite game. There are currently eight levels in total, with each level having very different maps, monsters, and bosses. How will you take on these different enemies with their different styles of fighting?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/1469055a0693e279dcc05368d600d7b1.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are hundreds of items in the game with no limit to the number of items you can take, so there's no need to worry about carrying to many of any one item. You can equip items as you wish and use them as main items in conjunction with character talents to form your own unique build as you bravely venture forth into the world of Portal Dungeon!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.poster.avif?t=1765534420\" width=616 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.webm?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1679220/extras/f21b8260257d36967ea1333134fbe469.mp4?t=1765534420\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Supports single player and up to 4 players connected online. It's more fun to take on the dungeon with friends!",
